              <h1> 3. Skip Fertilization for Houseplants if You're Unsure</h1>
              <p>Houseplants don't require fertilization unless they are struggling to grow. If you're unsure of how much or what type of fertilization to use when planting, it's better to skip that step altogether.<span id="dots">...</span><span id="more"></span> Too much fertilization may actually end up killing your plant rather than helping it.</span></p>

              <button onclick="myFunction()" id="myBtn">Read more</button>

