              <h1>4. Smaller Plants Are the Fastest Growing Plants</h1>
              <p>When buying your chosen plant, it's always better to purchase a smaller plant over a larger one. This is because a smaller plant will be able to get more established in its home and have a larger ratio of roots to top growth<span id="dots">...</span><span id="more"></span>. A larger plant will not continue to grow until its roots catch up with the top growth</span>.</p>

              <button onclick="myFunction()" id="myBtn">Read more</button>

